OL,6,CG2022FThe BBC announces it plans to
OL,7,Fmerge the UK BBC News channel and its
OL,8,Finternational counterpart, BBC World
OL,9,FNews. The corporation says the combined
OL,10,Fchannel - to be known as BBC News -
OL,11,Fwill launch in April 2023.
